dbQuery.sql: Select kpi_result.result_id , kpi_result.academic_year , kpi_result.month_id , kpi_result.org_id , kpi_result.org_name , kpi_result.kpi_level_id , kpi_result.kpi_level_name , kpi_result.kpi_group_id , kpi_result.kpi_group_short_name , kpi_result.kpi_group_name , kpi_result.kpi_structure_id , kpi_result.kpi_structure_name , kpi_result.kpi_type_id , kpi_result.kpi_type_name , kpi_result.kpi_type_short_name , kpi_result.kpi_id , kpi_result.kpi_name , kpi_result.formula_desc , kpi_result.calendar_type_name , kpi_result.period_name , kpi_result.kpi_uom_id , kpi_result.kpi_uom_name , kpi_result.multiplicand1_value , kpi_result.operator , kpi_result.multiplicand2_value , kpi_result.denominatorm_value , kpi_result.criteria_type_id , kpi_result.benchmark_value , kpi_result.target_value , kpi_result.actual_value , kpi_result.percent_actual_vs_target , kpi_result.percent_actual_change , kpi_result.score From [che].kpi_result kpi_result

Select sys_month.month_id, sys_month.calendar_year, sys_month.academic_year, sys_month.fiscal_year, sys_month.calendar_month_no, sys_month.academic_month_no, sys_month.fiscal_month_no, sys_month.th_month_name, sys_month.calendar2month, sys_month.calendar3month, sys_month.calendar4month, sys_month.calendar5month, sys_month.calendar6month, sys_month.calendar7month, sys_month.calendar8month, sys_month.calendar9month, sys_month.calendar10month, sys_month.calendar11month, sys_month.calendar12month, sys_month.academic2month, sys_month.academic3month, sys_month.academic4month, sys_month.academic5month, sys_month.academic6month, sys_month.academic7month, sys_month.academic8month, sys_month.academic9month, sys_month.academic10month, sys_month.academic11month, sys_month.academic12month, sys_month.fiscal2month, sys_month.fiscal3month, sys_month.fiscal4month, sys_month.fiscal5month, sys_month.fiscal6month, sys_month.fiscal7month, sys_month.fiscal8month, sys_month.fiscal9month, sys_month.fiscal10month, sys_month.fiscal11month, sys_month.fiscal12month From [che].sys_month as sys_month

Select kpi_structure.kpi_structure_id, kpi_structure.academic_year, kpi_structure.kpi_structure_name, kpi_structure.kpi_group_id, kpi_structure.structure_type_id From [che].kpi_structure as kpi_structure
Select kpi_type.kpi_type_id, kpi_type.academic_year, kpi_type.kpi_type_name, kpi_type.kpi_type_short_name From [che].kpi_type as kpi_type

Select qualitative_criteria.academic_year , qualitative_criteria.kpi_id , qualitative_criteria.criteria_group_detail_id , qualitative_criteria.cds_id , qualitative_criteria.criteria_desc, GROUP_CONCAT(distinct(running_no) ORDER BY running_no SEPARATOR ',') as qualitative From qualitative_criteria join kpi_result_detail on qualitative_criteria.criteria_id = kpi_result_detail.criteria_id where action_flag = 1 GROUP BY kpi_id
Select kpi_level.kpi_level_id , kpi_level.academic_year , kpi_level.kpi_level_name From kpi_level kpi_level

dbQuery.sql: select g.calendar_type_id ,g.calendar_type_name ,g.calendar_year ,g.academic_year ,g.fiscal_year ,g.calendar_month_no ,g.academic_month_no ,g.fiscal_month_no ,g.th_month_name ,g.kpi_group_id ,g.kpi_group_short_name ,g.kpi_level_id ,g.kpi_level_name ,e.kpi_type_id ,e.kpi_type_short_name ,g.path ,g.org_id ,g.org_name ,g.university_code ,g.university_name ,CASE WHEN g.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN university_code ELSE faculty_code END as faculty_code ,CASE WHEN g.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN university_name ELSE faculty_name END as faculty_name ,g.course_code ,g.course_name ,g.kpi_structure_id ,g.kpi_structure_name ,g.count_kpi ,g.score_criteria_flag ,CASE WHEN g.score_criteria_flag = 0 THEN null ELSE e.avg_score_kpi END as avg_score_kpi ,CASE WHEN g.score_criteria_flag = 0 THEN null ELSE g.avg_score_kpi_structure_id END as avg_score_kpi_structure_id ,CASE WHEN g.score_criteria_flag = 0 THEN case WHEN g.avg_score_kpi_structure_id = 5 THEN 'หลักสูตรได้มาตรฐาน' ELSE 'หลักสูตรไม่ได้มาตรฐาน' END ELSE (select threshold_name from threshold where academic_year = g.academic_year and kpi_level_id = g.kpi_level_id and (begin_threshold <= g.avg_score_kpi_structure_id and end_threshold >= g.avg_score_kpi_structure_id) ) END as kpi_structure_id_threshold_name from ( select kr.month_id ,kpi.calendar_type_id ,kr.calendar_type_name ,sm.calendar_year ,sm.academic_year ,sm.fiscal_year ,sm.calendar_month_no ,sm.academic_month_no ,sm.fiscal_month_no ,sm.th_month_name ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,org.path ,org.org_name ,org.university_code ,org.university_name ,org.faculty_code ,org.faculty_name ,org.course_code ,org.course_name ,kr.kpi_group_short_name ,kr.kpi_level_name ,kr.kpi_structure_name ,kpi.score_criteria_flag ,count(kr.kpi_id) as count_kpi ,ROUND(sum(kr.score)/count(kr.kpi_id),2) as avg_score_kpi_structure_id from kpi_result kr inner join sys_month sm on sm.month_id = kr.month_id inner join org on org.org_id = kr.org_id inner join kpi on kpi.kpi_id = kr.kpi_id group by kr.month_id ,kpi.calendar_type_id ,kr.calendar_type_name ,sm.calendar_year ,sm.academic_year ,sm.fiscal_year ,sm.calendar_month_no ,sm.academic_month_no ,sm.fiscal_month_no ,sm.th_month_name ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,org.path ,org.org_name ,org.university_code ,org.university_name ,org.faculty_code ,org.faculty_name ,org.course_code ,org.course_name ,kr.kpi_group_short_name ,kr.kpi_level_name ,kr.kpi_structure_name ,kpi.score_criteria_flag )g left join ( select kpis.month_id ,kpis.kpi_group_id ,kpis.kpi_level_id ,kpis.org_id ,kskt.kpi_structure_id ,kskt.kpi_type_id ,kskt.kpi_type_short_name ,coalesce(avg_score_kpi, 0) as avg_score_kpi from( select ks.kpi_structure_id , ks.kpi_structure_name , kt.kpi_type_id , kt.kpi_type_short_name from kpi_type kt, kpi_structure ks group by ks.kpi_structure_id , ks.kpi_structure_name , kt.kpi_type_id , kt.kpi_type_short_name )kskt left join ( select kr.month_id ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,kr.kpi_type_id ,ROUND(sum(score)/count(kr.kpi_type_id),2) as avg_score_kpi from kpi_result kr group by kr.month_id ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,kr.kpi_type_id ) kpis on kpis.kpi_structure_id = kskt.kpi_structure_id and kpis.kpi_type_id = kskt.kpi_type_id group by kpis.month_id ,kpis.kpi_group_id ,kpis.kpi_level_id ,kpis.org_id ,kskt.kpi_structure_id ,kskt.kpi_type_id ,kskt.kpi_type_short_name )e on e.month_id = g.month_id and e.kpi_group_id = g.kpi_group_id and e.kpi_level_id = g.kpi_level_id and e.org_id = g.org_id and e.kpi_structure_id = g.kpi_structure_id group by g.calendar_type_id ,g.calendar_type_name ,g.calendar_year ,g.academic_year ,g.fiscal_year ,g.calendar_month_no ,g.academic_month_no ,g.fiscal_month_no ,g.th_month_name ,g.kpi_group_id ,g.kpi_group_short_name ,g.kpi_level_id ,g.kpi_level_name ,e.kpi_type_id ,e.kpi_type_short_name ,g.path ,g.org_id ,g.org_name ,g.university_code ,g.university_name ,CASE WHEN g.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN university_code ELSE faculty_code END ,CASE WHEN g.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN university_name ELSE faculty_name END ,g.course_code ,g.course_name ,g.kpi_structure_id ,g.kpi_structure_name ,g.count_kpi ,g.score_criteria_flag

select kr.month_id ,kpi.calendar_type_id ,kr.calendar_type_name ,sm.calendar_year ,sm.academic_year ,sm.fiscal_year ,sm.calendar_month_no ,sm.academic_month_no ,sm.fiscal_month_no ,sm.th_month_name ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_group_name ,kr.kpi_group_short_name ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,kr.kpi_structure_name ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.kpi_level_name ,org.path ,kr.org_id ,kr.org_name ,org.university_code ,org.university_name ,CASE WHEN kr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_code ELSE org.faculty_code END as faculty_code ,CASE WHEN kr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_name ELSE org.faculty_name END as faculty_name ,org.course_code ,org.course_name ,kr.kpi_id ,kr.kpi_name ,kr.kpi_uom_name ,kr.target_value ,kr.multiplicand ,kr.denominator as denominatorm ,CASE WHEN kr.criteria_type_id = 2 THEN concat(kr.actual_value,' (',kpiqua.qualitative,')') ELSE kr.actual_value END as val ,kr.score as kpi_score ,orgstr.kpi_structure_score from kpi_result kr inner join org on org.org_id = kr.org_id inner join kpi on kpi.kpi_id = kr.kpi_id inner join sys_month sm on kr.month_id = sm.month_id left join (select ksr.month_id ,ksr.kpi_group_id ,ksr.kpi_level_id ,ksr.org_id ,ksr.kpi_structure_id ,ksr.score as kpi_structure_score from org_structure_result ksr )orgstr on orgstr.month_id = kr.month_id and orgstr.kpi_group_id = kr.kpi_group_id and orgstr.kpi_level_id = kr.kpi_level_id and orgstr.org_id = kr.org_id and orgstr.kpi_structure_id = kr.kpi_structure_id left join (select kr.month_id ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_id , GROUP_CONCAT(qc.running_no ORDER BY qc.running_no SEPARATOR ',') as qualitative from kpi_result kr, kpi_result_detail kpird, qualitative_criteria qc where kr.result_id = kpird.result_id and kpird.criteria_id = qc.criteria_id and action_flag = 1 GROUP BY kr.month_id ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_id )kpiqua on kpiqua.month_id = kr.month_id and kpiqua.kpi_group_id = kr.kpi_group_id and kpiqua.kpi_level_id = kr.kpi_level_id and kpiqua.org_id = kr.org_id and kpiqua.kpi_id = kr.kpi_id order by kr.month_id ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_id

select threshold.academic_year ,threshold.kpi_level_id ,lv.kpi_level_name ,threshold.threshold_name ,threshold.begin_threshold ,threshold.end_threshold ,CONCAT (begin_threshold, '-', end_threshold,' ', threshold_name) as Threshold from threshold left join kpi_level lv on lv.kpi_level_id = threshold.kpi_level_id

queryItem.expression: Count([Datasoure].[kpi_result].[kpi_id] for [Datasoure].[kpi_result].[kpi_structure_id],[Datasoure].[kpi_result].[kpi_level_id],[Model].[Data for Report].[KPI Type id] )

queryItem.name: Threshold short Name
queryItem.expression: Case When ([Model].[Threshold].[kpi_level_id] = [Model].[Data for Report].[KPI Level id] and [Model].[Data for Report].[Score] >= [Model].[Threshold].[begin_threshold] and [Model].[Data for Report].[Score] <= [Model].[Threshold].[end_threshold] ) Then ([Model].[Threshold].[threshold_short_name] ) Else ('NA') End

dbQuery.sql: select orgsr.month_id , kpi.calendar_type_id , ct.calendar_type_name , sys.calendar_year , sys.academic_year , sys.fiscal_year , sys.calendar_month_no , sys.academic_month_no , sys.fiscal_month_no , sys.th_month_name , kpi_group_short_name , orgsr.kpi_level_id , orgsr.kpi_level_name , orgsr.org_id , trim(orgsr.org_name) as org_name , org.path , org.university_code , org.university_name , CASE WHEN orgsr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_code ELSE org.faculty_code END as faculty_code , CASE WHEN orgsr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_name ELSE org.faculty_name END as faculty_name , org.course_code , org.course_name , orgsr.kpi_structure_id , orgsr.kpi_structure_name , orgsr.score as score_structure , orgsr.threshold_name , trim(substr(orgsr.threshold_name,18,5)) as threshold_short_name , ore.score_org from org_structure_result orgsr , sys_month sys , kpi_group kgro , org , ( select ore.month_id , org_id , score as score_org from org_result ore ) ore , kpi , calendar_type ct where orgsr.month_id = sys.month_id and orgsr.kpi_group_id = kgro.kpi_group_id and orgsr.org_id = org.org_id and orgsr.org_id = ore.org_id and sys.month_id = ore.month_id and orgsr.kpi_structure_id = kpi.kpi_structure_id and ct.calendar_type_id = kpi.calendar_type_id group by orgsr.month_id , kpi.calendar_type_id , ct.calendar_type_name , sys.calendar_year , sys.academic_year , sys.fiscal_year , sys.calendar_month_no , sys.academic_month_no , sys.fiscal_month_no , sys.th_month_name , kpi_group_short_name , orgsr.kpi_level_id , orgsr.kpi_level_name , orgsr.org_id , trim(orgsr.org_name) , org.path , org.university_code , org.university_name , CASE WHEN orgsr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_code ELSE org.faculty_code END , CASE WHEN orgsr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_name ELSE org.faculty_name END , org.course_code , org.course_name , orgsr.kpi_structure_id , orgsr.kpi_structure_name , orgsr.score , orgsr.threshold_name , trim(substr(orgsr.threshold_name,18,5)) , ore.score_org

select th.academic_year ,th.kpi_level_id ,lv.kpi_level_name ,CONCAT (th.begin_threshold, '-', th.end_threshold,' ', th.threshold_name) as threshold from threshold th, kpi_level lv where th.kpi_level_id = lv.kpi_level_id order by th.kpi_level_id

select kr.month_id ,kpi.calendar_type_id ,kr.calendar_type_name ,sm.calendar_year ,sm.academic_year ,sm.fiscal_year ,sm.calendar_month_no ,sm.academic_month_no ,sm.fiscal_month_no ,sm.th_month_name ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,kr.kpi_structure_name ,kr.kpi_id ,kr.kpi_name ,org.path ,kr.org_id ,kr.org_name ,org.university_code ,org.university_name ,CASE WHEN kr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_code ELSE org.faculty_code END as faculty_code ,CASE WHEN kr.kpi_level_id = 1 THEN org.university_name ELSE org.faculty_name END as faculty_name ,org.course_code ,org.course_name ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.kpi_level_name ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_group_name ,kr.kpi_group_short_name ,kr.formula_desc ,kr.period_name ,kr.kpi_uom_name ,kr.benchmark_value ,kr.target_value ,kr.actual_value ,kr.percent_actual_vs_target ,kr.percent_actual_change ,kr.score as kpi_score ,kpi.min_score from kpi_result kr, sys_month sm, org , kpi where kr.month_id = sm.month_id and org.org_id = kr.org_id and kpi.kpi_id = kr.kpi_id order by kr.academic_year ,sm.academic_month_no ,kr.kpi_group_id ,kr.kpi_level_id ,kr.org_id ,kr.kpi_structure_id ,kr.kpi_id

select month_id ,calendar_type_id ,calendar_type_name ,calendar_year ,academic_year ,fiscal_year ,calendar_month_no ,academic_month_no ,fiscal_month_no ,th_month_name ,no_of_month ,caseMonth ,org_id ,org_name ,kpi_group_id ,kpi_group_short_name ,kpi_level_id ,kpi_level_name ,kpi_structure_id ,kpi_structure_name ,kpi_id ,kpi_name ,cds_name ,support_data_name ,running_no ,evidence_flag ,cds_value ,evidence_path ,row_type ,created_by FROM ( select cdsre.month_id ,kpi.calendar_type_id ,ct.calendar_type_name ,sm.calendar_year ,sm.academic_year ,sm.fiscal_year ,sm.calendar_month_no ,sm.academic_month_no ,sm.fiscal_month_no ,sm.th_month_name ,per.no_of_month ,kpi.kpi_group_id ,kpi_group_short_name ,kpi.kpi_structure_id ,kpi_structure.kpi_structure_name ,CASE WHEN kpi.calendar_type_id = 1 THEN CASE WHEN per.no_of_month = 1 THEN th_month_name WHEN per.no_of_month = 2 THEN calendar2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 3 THEN calendar3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 4 THEN calendar4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 5 THEN calendar5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 6 THEN calendar6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 7 THEN calendar2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 8 THEN calendar3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 9 THEN calendar4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 10 THEN calendar5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN calendar6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN calendar6month END WHEN kpi.calendar_type_id = 2 THEN CASE WHEN per.no_of_month = 1 THEN th_month_name WHEN per.no_of_month = 2 THEN academic2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 3 THEN academic3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 4 THEN academic4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 5 THEN academic5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 6 THEN academic6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 7 THEN academic2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 8 THEN academic3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 9 THEN academic4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 10 THEN academic5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN academic6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN academic6month END WHEN kpi.calendar_type_id = 3 THEN CASE WHEN per.no_of_month = 1 THEN th_month_name WHEN per.no_of_month = 2 THEN fiscal2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 3 THEN fiscal3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 4 THEN fiscal4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 5 THEN fiscal5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 6 THEN fiscal6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 7 THEN fiscal2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 8 THEN fiscal3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 9 THEN fiscal4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 10 THEN fiscal5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN fiscal6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN fiscal6month END END as caseMonth ,kpi.kpi_level_id ,lv.kpi_level_name ,cdsre.org_id ,org.org_name ,map.kpi_id ,kpi.kpi_name ,cds.cds_name ,support_data_name ,map.cds_id as running_no ,evidence_flag ,cds_value ,evidence_path ,row_type ,cdev.created_by from kpi_cds_mapping map left join kpi on map.kpi_id = kpi.kpi_id left join kpi_group on kpi_group.kpi_group_id = kpi.kpi_group_id left join kpi_structure on kpi_structure.kpi_structure_id = kpi.kpi_structure_id left join cds on map.cds_id = cds.cds_id left join cds_result cdsre on cds.cds_id = cdsre.cds_id left join sys_month sm on sm.month_id = cdsre.month_id left join kpi_level lv on kpi.kpi_level_id = lv.kpi_level_id left join org on org.org_id = cdsre.org_id left join cds_result_detail cdsrede on cdsrede.result_id = cdsre.result_id left join cds_evidence cdev on cdev.result_detail_id = cdsrede.result_detail_id left join period per on per.period_id = kpi.period_id left join calendar_type ct on ct.calendar_type_id = kpi.calendar_type_id
UNION
select kre.month_id ,kpi.calendar_type_id ,kre.calendar_type_name ,sm.calendar_year ,sm.academic_year ,sm.fiscal_year ,sm.calendar_month_no ,sm.academic_month_no ,sm.fiscal_month_no ,sm.th_month_name ,'' as no_of_month ,kre.kpi_group_id ,kpi_group_short_name ,kre.kpi_structure_id ,kpi_structure_name ,th_month_name as caseMonth ,kre.kpi_level_id ,kre.kpi_level_name ,kre.org_id ,kre.org_name ,kre.kpi_id ,kre.kpi_name ,criteria_desc as cds_name ,'' as support_data_name ,running_no ,evidence_flag ,0 as cds_value ,evidence_path ,null as row_type ,ke.created_by from kpi_result kre, kpi_result_detail kred, qualitative_criteria qc, kpi_evidence ke , sys_month sm , kpi where kre.result_id = kred.result_id and kred.criteria_id = qc.criteria_id and kred.result_detail_id = ke.result_detail_id and kre.month_id = sm.month_id and kpi.kpi_id = kre.kpi_id and kred.action_flag = '1' )g

,CASE WHEN kpi.calendar_type_id = 1 THEN CASE WHEN per.no_of_month = 1 THEN th_month_name WHEN per.no_of_month = 2 THEN calendar2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 3 THEN calendar3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 4 THEN calendar4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 5 THEN calendar5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 6 THEN calendar6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 7 THEN calendar2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 8 THEN calendar3month WHEN per.no_of_month = 9 THEN calendar4month WHEN per.no_of_month = 10 THEN calendar5month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN calendar6month WHEN per.no_of_month = 11 THEN calendar6month END WHEN kpi.calendar_type_id = 2 THEN CASE WHEN per.no_of_month = 1 THEN th_month_name WHEN per.no_of_month = 2 THEN academic2month WHEN per.no_of_month = 3 THEN academic3month WHEN per.no_of_month =
